    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay that makes sense. so if i'm trying to get a really good crust on a loaf of sourdough, should i be focusing more on the sugar content in the dough or just cranking the oven heat higher to hit that temp? basically how do i maximize the reaction?",
